36:02.990 --> 36:05.149
What's my...? Have you got BO?

36:05.150 --> 36:09.189
Have I got 41 nipples?
Have you got very tiny testes?

36:09.190 --> 36:12.109
It's like Braille
down there, Jeremy.

36:12.110 --> 36:14.110
LAUGHTER

36:15.590 --> 36:18.469
A very short novel.
That's what it is - Braille.

36:18.470 --> 36:19.710
Yeah, the whole system.

36:21.310 --> 36:24.269
Everybody has...
I have a lot of things wrong.

36:24.270 --> 36:26.349
I'm blind, I'm deaf,

36:26.350 --> 36:29.029
I've got no sense of smell
cos I have a cold,

36:29.030 --> 36:30.829
