36:30.830 --> 36:34.069
Thank you
for the tongue kiss earlier.

36:34.070 --> 36:36.189
LAUGHTER

36:36.190 --> 36:38.590
Just went deep with it, too!

36:39.790 --> 36:42.789
No, we all have crazy faults.

36:42.790 --> 36:45.589
My fault isn't
something horrendous, like,

36:45.590 --> 36:47.749
"I can't stop murdering children."

36:47.750 --> 36:51.269
LAUGHTER
I just can't stop.

36:51.270 --> 36:53.469
I like to think
I'm a horrible driver...

36:53.470 --> 36:55.509
Horrible or bad?

36:55.510 --> 36:59.349
I ride motorcycles everywhere, so
you can race up through traffic,

