in the Kia Cee-apostrophe-d.

38:01.030 --> 38:02.389
What was your goal?

38:02.390 --> 38:05.629
My goal was just to see if I could
drive a manual car.

38:05.630 --> 38:08.829
I haven't done that since high
school, so that was interesting.

38:08.830 --> 38:10.629
Really? Yeah.

