38:56.150 --> 39:00.389
'Now, keeping it tidy through
the lines there. Yes, pretty good.

39:00.390 --> 39:02.029
'Very good, actually.'

39:02.030 --> 39:03.429
Very good.

39:03.430 --> 39:06.709
'Are we going to be able
to find fourth?'

39:06.710 --> 39:10.509
Turn from hell coming up.

39:10.510 --> 39:12.669
'Oh, yeah, this turn,
not fun every time.'

39:12.670 --> 39:15.349
'That's almost beautiful.' 'Yeah.

39:15.350 --> 39:17.270
'That's what I call
the adult diaper.'

39:17.271 --> 39:18.989
'Whoa, that's cutting that one!

39:18.990 --> 39:21.909
'That's quite uncomfortable
at that speed.' 'Yeah.'

39:21.910 --> 39:26.629
'Look at it gripping. That's nicely
