39:26.630 --> 39:28.869
'And around Gambon.'

39:28.870 --> 39:32.349
There we are, ladies and gentlemen,
across the line! There we go!

39:32.350 --> 39:34.349
CHEERING AND APPLAUSE

39:34.350 --> 39:35.749
Wow!

39:35.750 --> 39:37.829
So...

39:37.830 --> 39:41.589
Where would you like to appear
on the board?

39:41.590 --> 39:44.229
I'm going to say
somewhere in the middle.

39:44.230 --> 39:47.669
Didn't you... Actually, I know you
did, cos you told our researchers,

39:47.670 --> 39:50.589
you were desperate,
cos you went back out...

39:50.590 --> 39:53.349
"Do you mind if I have another go?"
"Give me another shot."

39:53.350 --> 39:56.309
Cos you wanted to beat Tom Cruise.

