so it's not letting me slide.

46:17.030 --> 46:18.429
Foot hard down.

46:18.430 --> 46:21.357
Hard down, and it won't slide.

46:23.630 --> 46:26.389
That is the traction control on.

46:26.390 --> 46:28.429
Can I just say, that was BLEEP.

