GUNSHOTS

01:00:31.130 --> 01:00:33.050
GUNFIRE

01:00:44.010 --> 01:00:47.090
APPLAUSE

01:00:48.410 --> 01:00:50.449
Yeah!

01:00:50.450 --> 01:00:52.889
Come on! Yeah!

01:00:52.890 --> 01:00:55.849
Actually, it's not bad.
It's not bad at all.

01:00:55.850 --> 01:00:58.649
And on that bombshell,
it is time to end.

